title: War of the Spider Queen Condemnation
description:
War of the Spider Queen Book 3
Condemnation

Sorry for the seemingly extreme size of a simple audiobook but I could not find this file anywhere but Audible so I bought and downloaded the .aa file and am sharing with everyone as is my duty.

As I had to convert the .aa Audible file to MP3, the end result is two MP3 files approx. 390 mb each.

As you download, please scan the files and post clean, as it is.  Only the first two in the 5 book series are available until now and I would like to see the next two become available soon.
